'''Hindi Zahṛa''' d yiwet n [[Acennay|tcennayt]] [[Tamaziɣt]] tameqṛant, tlul asegwas n 1979 di Xuribga Tamurt n [[Merruk|Meṛṛuk]], tettidir di Fṛansa seg usegwas 1993, tcennu s tutlayt [[Taglizit]] d [[Tamaziɣt|Tmaziɣt]]/[[Tacelḥit]].

== Tameddurmant ==
{{...}}
Asegwas n 2010 tessufγed Hindi Zahṛa aḍebsi y ines amenzu ''Handmade'' itt yeǧǧan ad tawi araz Constantin 12 Nunber 2010, <ref>[http://next.liberation.fr/musique/01012301895-prix-constantin-qui-va-succeder-a-emily-loiseau ''Hindi Zahra, prix Constantin 2010''] sur ''[[Libération (journal)|Libération]] Next'' du 12 novembre 2010.</ref>.
Ass n tza di [[Fuṛaṛ]] usegwas 2011 tebwi ayen umi qqaren ''Victoires de la musique'' Aḍebsi id yufraren di Cna Umaḍal ''Handmade''.

